IMPORTANT — scope and provenance:
  This dataset is a compiled and normalized mapping (organ <-> gene, with risk
  and follow-up metadata) created by the author. CC BY 4.0 applies to THIS
  compilation and its graph representation — NOT to the underlying guideline
  source documents, whose copyright and terms of use remain with their
  respective publishers (RCC, EAU, et al.).

  This material is a reference / decision-support aid, not a clinical
  recommendation.
